---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About · OGENEO" active="about">
  <div class="about">
    <h1>A personal glimpse into my life.</h1>
    <p class="sub">The world through my eyes. My thoughts along the way.</p>
    <p class="muted">
      OgeneO is a private-first visual journal built around Moments rather than
      albums. Photos arrive straight from a phone's share sheet, first-person
      captures from Meta glasses carry their own glyph, and related Moments
      gather themselves into Experiences by time and place. Thoughts drift
      through the feed as handwritten comets.
    </p>
    <p class="sig">Gene</p>

    <details class="hood">
      <summary>
        <span class="car" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 64 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <!-- body -->
            <path d="M4 24 h4 M18 24 h20 M52 24 h6 c1 0 2-1 2-2 v-4 c0-2-2-3-4-3 l-10-1 -7-6 H22 l-6 6 -8 1 c-2 0.3-4 1.5-4 3.5 V22 c0 1 1 2 2 2" />
            <!-- open hood -->
            <path d="M40 8 L54 2 M40 8 l12.5 5.5" />
            <!-- wheels -->
            <circle cx="13" cy="24" r="4.5" />
            <circle cx="45" cy="24" r="4.5" />
            <!-- engine sparkle -->
            <path d="M46 8.5 l1 -2 1 2 2 .5 -2 1 -.5 2 -1.2 -1.7 -2 .2 z" stroke-width="1" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="label">Want to look under the hood?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </summary>

      <div class="engine">
        <h2>The pipeline</h2>
        <p>
          Share Sheet → iPhone Shortcut → Cloudflare Worker → Cloudinary →
          Apollo → this site. A photo shared from the camera roll posts to
          <code>/api/upload</code> with its original file and metadata; the
          Worker uploads the media to Cloudinary, enriches it, writes a Moment
          to the database, and it's live before the phone is back in the
          pocket. Comets travel a parallel lane through <code>/api/thought</code>,
          carrying GPS from the phone so each one can drop a pin.
        </p>

        <h2>The stack</h2>
        <p>
          The site is Astro rendered server-side on Cloudflare Workers, one
          worker for pages and API both. Data lives in Cloudflare D1, SQLite
          running at the edge. Media lives in Cloudinary and is delivered
          resized and format-negotiated (<code>f_auto,q_auto</code>) per
          device. Uploads authenticate with a bearer secret; media uploads are
          SHA-1 signed. The maps are Leaflet over CARTO dark tiles. Source
          lives on <a href="https://github.com/genearch/ogeneo">GitHub</a>,
          and every deploy is a <code>wrangler deploy</code> from main.
        </p>

        <h2>Apollo, the enrichment engine</h2>
        <p>
          Apollo is the journal's small brain. When a Moment lands, it reads
          the metadata the Shortcut sends — capture time, GPS, camera make and
          model, filename, caption — then infers tags from the caption, flags
          Lily appearances, and marks Meta glasses captures as first-person
          "Through My Eyes" Moments. Its main trick is grouping: a Moment
          within 8 hours and 30 km of related Moments joins their Experience;
          two loose Moments that close together found a new one, titled from
          place and date. V1 is honest arithmetic; the upgrade path is Workers
          AI reading captions, weather, and travel patterns.
        </p>

        <h2>The easter eggs</h2>
        <p>
          Anniversary resurfacing (a past year's Moment returns on its date),
          journey milestones at 10, 25, 50, 100+ Moments, rolling thought
          comets interleaved through the feed, and a Currently Wandering card
          driven by a settings row in D1.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about { max-width: 620px; margin: 8vh auto 0; padding: 0 12px; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 500; font-size: 40px; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .sub { font-family: var(--hand); font-size: 26px; color: var(--text-dim); margin: 0 0 22px; }
  .about > p.muted { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .sig { font-family: var(--hand); font-size: 30px; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 26px; }

  .hood { margin: 40px 0 60px; border-top: 1px solid var(--card-edge); padding-top: 26px; }
  .hood summary {
    list-style: none; cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .hood summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .hood summary:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .car { color: var(--gold); flex: 0 0 auto; display: inline-flex; }
  .car svg { width: 58px; height: 30px; }
  .label { font-family: var(--hand); font-size: 25px; }
  .chev { width: 20px; height: 20px; margin-left: auto; transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .hood[open] .chev { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  .engine { padding: 8px 4px 0; }
  .engine h2 {
    font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 500; font-size: 23px;
    color: var(--gold); margin: 26px 0 6px;
  }
  .engine p { margin: 0; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .engine a { color: var(--gold); border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--gold); }
  .engine code {
    font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--text);
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--card-edge);
    border-radius: 5px; padding: 1px 6px;
  }
</style>
